examples.en: She undertook the project late in her career.
He undertook to pay the money back in six months.
She undertook to complete the project in six months.
The researchers undertook a series of studies.
Dr Johnson undertook the task of writing a comprehensive English dictionary.
The special work which he undertook, and the rich ability with which he wrought it.
Under the coverture of a raging snowstorm, the rebels undertook their surprise attack on the fortress.
